HIGH-LEVEL ROADMAP
==================

  - Improve performance of icon cache

  - Create multi-window mode where submenus open in separate windows

  - Write XDG menu parser based on libmenu-cache (probably "jgmenu_run xdg2")

  - Add tint2 compatibility mode (i.e. read tint2rc file)
	config.h variables should be set in the following order:
	(i.e. bottom of list has higher precedence)
	  - default (config.c)
	  - jgmenurc (--config-file=)
	  - tint2rc (--tint2rc=)
	  - cmd line args (e.g. --icon_size=)

  - Pipemenus

  - Support for adding favourites in real-time (e.g. keyboard shortcut for
    locking menu-item onto the root menu - or similar)

  - Add support for "fixed-position" items such as icons/images and shapes

  - Add search box

  - Consider "hover" features and "inline expansion" of menus
